      <title>密歇根大学在特朗普压力下削减了DEI计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/university-of-michigan-scraps-dei-program-amid-trump-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[密歇根大学（University of Michigan）正在为特朗普政府施加压力放弃这种努力，并经过几个月的批评，并在其成本和有效性上批评了几个月后，就将其曾经宣布的多样性，公平和包容性计划取消。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/university-of-michigan-scraps-dei-program-amid-trump-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 00:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
